---
title: Bacon-Wrapped Chicken with Mexican-Style Street Corn Salad
description: Craving Mexican tonight? We've packed all the robust flavours of elotes – or, street corn – into a delicious charred corn and pepper side salad, topped with feta and a creamy chive dressing. It's the perfect companion for garlicky bacon-wrapped chicken!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-wrapped-chicken-a4f7d35f.jpg
